OL,3,C'A restriction of truth': Medics speak
OL,4,Cout after guilty verdict
OL,6,FThey explain: "This restriction of the
OL,7,Ftruth is not something that either of
OL,8,Fus are comfortable with and will be
OL,9,Fdiscussing with our employer when, and
OL,10,Fnot if, this information can be made
OL,11,Fpublic."
OL,13,FBoth men were convicted at Jersey's
OL,14,FRoyal Court of breaching health and
OL,15,Fsafety law following an eight-day
OL,16,Fjurats trial - they had denied any
OL,17,Fwrongdoing.
