OL,3,C'A restriction of truth': Medics speak
OL,4,Cout after guilty verdict
OL,6,FThe pair say they are "incredibly
OL,7,Fmoved and humbled by the support of
OL,8,Ffellow frontline workers, family,
OL,9,Ffriends and the public".
OL,11,FThey add: "It is a testament to the
OL,12,Fincredible character of our island
OL,13,Fcommunity that it has been our honour
OL,14,Fto serve."
OL,16,FMedics will hold a peaceful protest to
OL,17,Fstand in solidarity with their
OL,18,Fcolleagues outside Jersey's Ambulance
OL,19,FStation in St Helier at 6pm on Friday
OL,20,F28 June.
